Name:           Water Element
Short Name:     water
Level Required: 12

Description:
  Raw elemental Water in living form, the Water Element can engulf
  enemies and drown them, as well as hurl tidal wave spells.

Commands:
  - summon water:   Summons it to you         (costs 70 sp)
  - catt <monster>: Makes it attack <monster> (costs 10 sp)
  - cstop:          Makes it stop fighting    (costs 20 sp)
  - ban water:      Banishes it               (costs 30 sp)
